                  </persName>
             sworn.</p>
               <p>I am a pawnbroker: I have a pepper castor the prisoner pawned with me.</p>
               <p>[It was produced in Court, and deposed to by the prosecutor.]</p>
               <p>PRISONER's DEFENCE.</p>
               <p>I have several witnesses to my character, but they are not here.</p>
